        'meta_description' => 'A day-trip plan for Mangatarem Pangasinan covering Manleluag Spring Park warm sulfur pools, the forest trail, and the town center. DIY notes.',
        'tags' => 'Pangasinan, Mangatarem, Hot Springs, Day Trip, Nature',
