        'meta_title' => 'Tondol Beach Anda Pangasinan: The Low-Tide Sandbar Walk | Resort Guru PH',
        'meta_description' => 'A day-trip plan for Tondol Beach in Anda Pangasinan covering the one-kilometer low-tide sandbar walk, the town center, and overnight tips.',
