        'meta_title' => 'Bacnotan La Union: Pebble Beach and the Northern Quiet Side | Resort Guru PH',
        'meta_description' => 'A slow Bacnotan La Union weekend covering Pebble Beach, the old church plaza, the Baroro River, and the inland barangays. DIY notes from Manila.',
        'tags' => 'La Union, Bacnotan, Pebble Beach, North Luzon, Weekend',
