        'meta_title' => 'Argao Cebu: A Colonial Stop and the Torta Trail | Resort Guru PH',
        'meta_description' => 'A heritage day in Argao Cebu covering the 1734 church complex, the fortified wall, the bahay-na-bato walk, and the famous Cebu torta trail.',
