        'meta_title' => 'Anda Bohol: Quinale Beach and the Slow Eastern Side | Resort Guru PH',
        'meta_description' => 'A slow Anda Bohol weekend covering Quinale Beach, Cabagnow Cave Pool, Lamanok Island, and the eastern Bohol pace. DIY notes from Tagbilaran.',
        'tags' => 'Bohol, Anda, Quinale Beach, Cave Pool, Weekend',
