        'meta_title' => 'San Joaquin Iloilo: The Cuartel and Church Heritage Route | Resort Guru PH',
        'meta_description' => 'A half-day San Joaquin Iloilo heritage route covering the Battle of Tetuan church facade, the Cuartel de Santo Tomas ruins, the campo santo, and Punta Cana.',
